Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Sears Tower
Description: No, it is not Willis tower. I refuse to call it as such. Sears for life!

Name: The Apple Pan
Description: If you like pie or burgers, you are doing yourself a disservice by not checking out this LA staple.

Name: Jolly Oyster
Description: If you're driving up the Ventura coastline and feeling peckish, stop at this charming food truck for a delicious oyster feast along the California coast.

Name: Quebec
Description: One of the most french areas in our great brothers to the North. Has good Poutine.

Name: Graceland
Description: Once home of the great Elvis Presley. Now a museum. Eat a peanut butter banana and bacon sandwich for the man.
